          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Cross sections measured at 3 different temperatures",
                " in 3 different spectra: Reactor spectrum, Be-filtered",
                " spectrum, Bi-filtered spectrum. The characteristic",
                " energies of these spectra were deduced from the",
                " theoretical cross section values (Tab. 2 of AKE 12)",
                " and their theoretical energy dependence (Fig. 4):",
                "  Reactor spectrum: about 25 milli-eV,",
                "  Be-filtered beam: about 4 milli-eV,",
                "  Bi-filtered beam: about 1.3 milli-eV."
              ]
            }
          ],
